members.signatureBeforeChange: public Assignment(Expression lhs, Expression expression, int sourceEnd)
members.signatureAfterChange: public Assignment(Expression lhs, Expression expression, int sourceEnd)
diff: +		lhs.bits |= IsStrictlyAssignedMASK; // tag lhs as assigned

members.signatureBeforeChange: public CompoundAssignment(Expression lhs, Expression expression,int operator, int sourceEnd)
members.signatureAfterChange: public CompoundAssignment(Expression lhs, Expression expression,int operator, int sourceEnd)
diff: +	lhs.bits &= ~IsStrictlyAssignedMASK; // tag lhs as NON assigned - it is also a read access
